      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARK CINNAMON (8) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (21.10) at this track in a Grade 5. Lines up from box 8 for the first time. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Top prospect. EDDY SPAGHETTI (2) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 17 from 31 starts. Continues to race well, filling the minors at the last four starts, the latest when third (20.93) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Expected to be in the finish again. HEY ALDO (7) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from six starts. Missed the frame latest (19.72) when eighth over 340m at Bulli in a Grade 5. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SKETCHY STORY (4) cannot be ruled out.",
